{"tid":648906,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? $36.5/h 中年清潔工滿身勞損 每月醫療開支逾$2000","createTime":"2018-05-01T06:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T05:50:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9128945548c0976e9afd4b8e88d996f6adced01d","tid":648906,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"今日（5月1日）是勞動節，在獅子山下，許多勞工默默耕耘，背負着沉重的生活擔子，靠雙手養活自己，惟不少基層勞工被社會遺忘、唾棄，卻仍堅守崗位不辭勞苦為社會付出，賺取微薄薪金。<br />\n年逾50歲的陳女士（化名）為外判清潔工人，從事清潔工作逾十載，每天汗流浹背工作10小時，由清潔大廈垃圾房至把垃圾搬上垃圾車，都一手包辦。辛勞背後，她的月薪由4年前入職時<span style=\"color: red;\">8,750元，至今增加至9,450元，累計增加8%，但兩次都只是跟隨最低工資水平調整，惟調整後，時薪只有36.5元</span>，只略高於最低工資2元，生活過得絕不輕鬆。4年來實際時薪只加了3元，生活迫人，她直言：「我唔做就無錢開飯。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為工作滿身勞損　每月醫療開支逾$2000</span><br />\n<br />\n陳女士說，每次清理大廈垃圾時，都要用力把垃圾袋從垃圾筒抽出並放到槽口，日復日、年復年，重複的動作導致肩膊勞損：「（手）繞着個膠袋拉出嚟，可能拉嘅時候呢到（肩膊）好用力。」她更患上俗稱「彈弓手」的指屈肌腱鞘炎，每當手指彎曲便會感到痛楚，形容端着碗吃飯時，有部分手指會失去知覺和麻痺，須每周一次進行物理治療。<br />\n提到工作較吃力的部分，她斷言說把垃圾搬到垃圾車最辛苦，須使出全身力氣把垃圾抬上車，經常導致肌肉酸痛。除工作勞損外，陳女士亦做過大手術切除子宮，現時每天都須服食魚肝油來改善術後情況，每月醫療開支逾2,000元，負擔沉重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/183174/%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E7%AF%80-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%BB%BF%E8%BA%AB%E5%8B%9E%E6%90%8D-4%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%82%E8%96%AA%E5%83%85%E5%8A%A0-3-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%81%9A%E7%84%A1%E9%8C%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%A3%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F183174%2F%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%2590%258D-4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%258A%25A0-3-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%258C%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A3%25AF&d=hUgXkzpu5NMhDT%2FrcyqztqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=81ff0629\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/183174/%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E7%AF%80-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%BB%BF%E8%BA%AB%E5%8B%9E%E6%90%8D-4%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%82%E8%96%AA%E5%83%85%E5%8A%A0-3-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%81%9A%E7%84%A1%E9%8C%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%A3%AF</a>"},{"pid":"ba8a9942e08347c743886675ef4172b3b6342180","tid":648906,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1401921/org/b6eb268e735b0ef3c2a874d52c01fc60.jpg/Ulm4OuOQG-ZJ3Lc9ws07so2cA7dFiJZJi4dhj4uHYY8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1401921%2Forg%2Fb6eb268e735b0ef3c2a874d52c01fc60.jpg%2FUlm4OuOQG-ZJ3Lc9ws07so2cA7dFiJZJi4dhj4uHYY8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=976b9356&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6cf6fe1524310fe2495f1169a5ebf76100ac0c6","tid":648906,"uid":115211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"去做地盤雜工仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408279492e21602a2bc2c96efb03e1a21bc52e64","tid":648906,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6cf6fe1524310fe2495f1169a5ebf76100ac0c6","tid":648906,"uid":115211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"去做地盤雜工仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"梗係 食老綜最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2c6588fa075007ed1324b1b038f8413a4516d3","tid":648906,"uid":89350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"政府外判？ 幾時有人敢爭取公開政府判出去筆錢幾多<br />\n中間比人食左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da018191fc42c7df9b0b2d77e9fe62c4098ecbe4","tid":648906,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=